<title>Fire Mana<>

<content>
    <section> Introduction <>
        <p>Fire mana is a category of mana which is harvested from any kind of fire. People
        who master fire mana can create and eject large volumes of heat and fire.<>
        <p>Fire mana has a weak affinity with <a t="#mana_*_lava">#<>.<>

    <section> Archetypes <>
        <heading level="1">Fire Caster<>
        <p>Fire casters are pretty singular in what they do: they cast flames in different arrays and pattern
        to burn and immolate their opponents.<>
        <p>In the presence of flames, fire casters can manipulate flames as well as emitting their own attacks.<>

        <heading level="1">Fire Animators<>
        <p>Fire <a t="#mana_*_animators">animators<> can create fire elementals to do their bidding. Fire elementals
        do not have much substance, but are fast and can emit deadly fire attacks.<>
        <p>In the presence of flames, fire casters can manipulate flames as well as emitting their own attacks.<>
<>